nishita-jain.content: Nishita is a sophomore in the Jerome Fisher Program in Management and Technology studying Computer Science and Management. Along with Hack4Impact, Nishita is a member of Social Impact Consulting and Penn Blockchain. When found not coding (gasp!), Nishita is most likely reading about decentralized technology, eating unhealthy foods, or playing Catan!
